            , productid
            , orderqty
            , unitprice
            , unitpricediscount
            , case
                when unitpricediscount > 0 then true
                else false
            end as had_discount
            , greatest(coalesce(unitprice * coalesce(unitpricediscount, 0.0) * orderqty, 0.0), 0.0) as total_discount
            , greatest(coalesce(unitprice * orderqty, 0.0), 0.0) as total_gross
